{%- comment -%}
  Notification Preferences / What to Expect Email (FULL HTML)
  - Locale normalization + RTL detection
  - COUNTRY-BASED locale resolution (same as Price Alerts)
  - Headline above hero (purple, 48px) + desktop/mobile hero images
  - Body copy: subheading, purple-tick list (4 items), body2, body3, CTA "Set my preferences"
